<plot>John, a down's syndrome child, helps build the family cottage, plays with his pet rabbit, and has a happy childhood. His Mum dies and he is separated from his family for 45 years. He escapes from an Alzheimer's lock-down ward and crosses the country to rejoin his brother and extended family.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?278582</url></doc>
